---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI Use Case Checklists | Scott Armbruster" description="Structured evaluation checklists for choosing the right AI tools. Compare options for general AI, code assistants, document analysis, image generation, and meeting transcription.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-blue-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase mb-6">
        <a href="/resources" class="hover:text-white transition">Resources</a>
        <span class="mx-2 text-slate-600">/</span>
        <a href="/resources/shadow-ai-governance-toolkit" class="hover:text-white transition">Governance Toolkit</a>
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        AI Use Case Checklists
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        Every business is different. These checklists walk you through the specific factors that matter for your organization -- industry, team size, compliance requirements, existing tech stack, and budget -- so you land on the right tool instead of the most popular one.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-400 mb-8">
        Each checklist is designed to pair with the <a href="/resources/shadow-ai-governance-toolkit" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-white transition">Shadow AI Governance Toolkit</a>. Use them during Week 2 when you're selecting your approved tool stack.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Checklists Grid -->
  <section class="pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="space-y-6">

        <!-- General AI Assistant -->
        <a href="/resources/use-case-checklists/general-ai-assistant" class="group bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/40 transition block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold group-hover:text-blue-400 transition">General AI Assistant</h2>
                <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-semibold bg-slate-800 px-2 py-1 rounded">FOUNDATION TOOL</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-3">Evaluate Claude Team, Gemini Business, ChatGPT Team, M365 Copilot, and local open-source options based on your industry, compliance requirements, existing tech stack, and team size.</p>
              <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white font-semibold text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2 transition">
                Open Checklist
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Code Assistant -->
        <a href="/resources/use-case-checklists/code-assistant" class="group bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/40 transition block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold group-hover:text-blue-400 transition">Code Assistant</h2>
                <span class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-semibold bg-slate-800 px-2 py-1 rounded">DEV TEAMS ONLY</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-3">Compare Claude Code, Codex, GitHub Copilot, and Cursor Team based on your language stack, repo size, security posture, budget, and pricing model preferences.</p>
              <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white font-semibold text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2 transition">
                Open Checklist
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Document Analysis -->
        <a href="/resources/use-case-checklists/document-analysis" class="group bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/40 transition block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold group-hover:text-blue-400 transition">Document Analysis</h2>
                <span class="text-xs text-green-500 font-semibold bg-green-600/10 px-2 py-1 rounded">REUSE OPPORTUNITY</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-3">Determine whether you need a dedicated document analysis tool or can reuse your General AI Assistant, based on document types, compliance needs, and processing volume.</p>
              <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white font-semibold text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2 transition">
                Open Checklist
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Image Generation -->
        <a href="/resources/use-case-checklists/image-generation" class="group bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/40 transition block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold group-hover:text-blue-400 transition">Image Generation</h2>
                <span class="text-xs text-green-500 font-semibold bg-green-600/10 px-2 py-1 rounded">REUSE OPPORTUNITY</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-3">Decide whether built-in image generation from your General AI Assistant is sufficient or if you need a specialist tool like MidJourney, based on creative volume, brand guidelines, and quality requirements.</p>
              <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white font-semibold text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2 transition">
                Open Checklist
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Meeting Transcription -->
        <a href="/resources/use-case-checklists/meeting-transcription" class="group bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-blue-500/40 transition block">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold group-hover:text-blue-400 transition">Meeting Transcription</h2>
                <span class="text-xs text-yellow-500 font-semibold bg-yellow-600/10 px-2 py-1 rounded">CHECK EXISTING TOOLS</span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-3">Audit your existing meeting platform capabilities before adding a dedicated transcription tool. Evaluate based on your meeting platform, recording policies, and data sensitivity requirements.</p>
              <span class="text-blue-400 group-hover:text-white font-semibold text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2 transition">
                Open Checklist
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>

      <!-- Back link -->
      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800/60">
        <a href="/resources/shadow-ai-governance-toolkit" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-white font-semibold text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2 transition">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 16l-4-4m0 0l4-4m-4 4h18"/>
          </svg>
          Back to Shadow AI Governance Toolkit
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
